            {
              "message": "You are an expense parser.\n\nExtract:\n\n* amount\n* category\n* note\n* date\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON.\n\nCategories allowed:\n\n* Food\n* Travel\n* Shopping\n* Entertainment\n* Bills\n* Health\n* Other\n\nRules:\n\n* If category is unclear, use \"Other\".\n* Date must be in YYYY-MM-DD format.\n* If the user does not mention a date, use this date: {{ $now.format('yyyy-MM-dd') }}\n\nReturn format:\n{\n\"amount\": number,\n\"category\": \"string\",\n\"note\": \"string\",\n\"date\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\"\n}\n"
            }
          ]
        },
        "batching": {}
      },
